    "2323203": {
      "type": "contentBlock",
      "enabled": true,
      "collapsed": false,
      "level": 1,
      "fields": {
        "headingSection": "Secure Remote Access for Employees, Vendors, and Service Desks",
        "headingSwitch": false,
        "bodyRedactorRestricted": null,
        "ctaLink": "{\"linkedId\":null,\"linkedSiteId\":null,\"linkedTitle\":null,\"linkedUrl\":null,\"payload\":null,\"type\":\"entry\"}",
        "label": null,
        "contentSubsections": {
          "2450839": {
            "type": "contentWithAsset",
            "enabled": true,
            "collapsed": false,
            "fields": {
              "heading": null,
              "body": "<p>Traditional remote access methods, like RDP and VPNs, lack granular access management controls and deep visibility into session activity. Their security deficiencies can leave organizations vulnerable to exploits via stolen credentials, session hijacking, and other attacks. These issues also make VPNs a particularly poor choice for vendor access.</p>\n<p>With<strong> BeyondTrust Secure Remote Access solutions:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Apply robust least privilege and audit controls to all remote access from employees, vendors, and service desks.</li></ul>\n<ul><li>Benefit from two VPN-less solutions:<strong> <a href=\"{entry:503393@1:url||https://bluetext.beyondtrust.com/products/privileged-remote-access}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Privileged Remote Access</a> </strong>and <strong><a href=\"{entry:501290@1:url||https://bluetext.beyondtrust.com/products/remote-support}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Remote Support</a></strong>, built for specific use cases. Each solution is a security leader in its class, while providing powerful productivity enhancement features.</li></ul>\n<ul><li>Get comprehensive capabilities from the start, including security essentials, such as MFA, SSO, and SAML integrations.</li></ul>",
              "asset": [],
              "resource": [
                2448451
              ],
              "ctaLink": "{\"linkedId\":null,\"linkedSiteId\":null,\"linkedTitle\":null,\"linkedUrl\":null,\"payload\":null,\"type\":\"entry\"}",
              "linkText": null,
              "contentAlignment": true,
              "contentTheme": "whiteTheme",
              "sidebarEnabled": false
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
