    "2323243": {
      "type": "contentBlock",
      "enabled": true,
      "collapsed": false,
      "level": 1,
      "fields": {
        "headingSection": "Secure Remote Support for Service Desks",
        "headingSwitch": false,
        "bodyRedactorRestricted": "<p>Service desks need more complete remote support solutions to solve an expanding list of use cases while meeting high standards for issue resolution. In addition, service desks are targeted by attackers because of their sensitive access and need robust security features that won’t take valuable time and resources to implement. </p>\n<p>BeyondTrust Remote Support is a single, holistic solution built to support every device and improve service desk workflows, while also providing robust security. Enable your help desk and ITSM teams to:</p>\n<ul class=\"checkmark\"><li>Securely access and fix any remote device, on any platform, anywhere in the world. </li></ul>\n<ul class=\"checkmark\"><li>Adhere to ITSM best practices.</li></ul>\n<ul class=\"checkmark\"><li>Work seamlessly with technologies such as ServiceNow, Jira Service Manager, Zendesk, and Microsoft Teams, improving both the user and technician experience.<br /></li></ul>",
        "ctaLink": "{\"linkedUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.beyondtrust.com\\/products\\/remote-support\",\"linkedId\":null,\"linkedSiteId\":null,\"linkedTitle\":null,\"payload\":\"{\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\"}\",\"type\":\"url\"}",
        "label": "Learn more",
        "contentSubsections": []
      }
    },
