    "2323325": {
      "type": "contentBlock",
      "enabled": true,
      "collapsed": false,
      "level": 1,
      "fields": {
        "headingSection": "Zero Trust Remote Access",
        "headingSwitch": false,
        "bodyRedactorRestricted": "<p>BeyondTrust Secure Remote Access is engineered with robust security controls and helps enable zero trust principles, zero trust architectures (ZTA), and zero trust network access (ZTNA) by enforcing least privilege, implementing segmentation, isolating assets, and monitoring and managing sessions. The solution also enables a just-in-time access model, with MFA and the option for per-session MFA, to reduce risk related to standing privileges.</p>",
        "ctaLink": "{\"linkedUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.beyondtrust.com\\/solutions\\/zero-trust\",\"linkedId\":null,\"linkedSiteId\":null,\"linkedTitle\":null,\"payload\":\"{\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\"}\",\"type\":\"url\"}",
        "label": "Learn more",
        "contentSubsections": {
          "2450848": {
            "type": "contentWithAsset",
            "enabled": true,
            "collapsed": false,
            "fields": {
              "heading": "FedRAMP® Authorized Secure Remote Access Solution",
              "body": "<p>BeyondTrust is FedRAMP® authorized to operate (ATO) at the moderate impact level for its Secure Remote Access (SRA) solutions, which include Remote Support and Privileged Remote Access. Your organization can fulfill the Federal Government's <a href=\"https://www.fedramp.gov/assets/resources/documents/FedRAMP_Policy_Memo.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.fedramp.gov/assets/resources/documents/FedRAMP_Policy_Memo.pdf\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cloud Computing Mandate</a> by using BeyondTrust's FedRAMP® Moderate authorized solutions.</p>",
              "asset": [
                2366917
              ],
              "resource": [],
              "ctaLink": "{\"linkedId\":1383336,\"linkedSiteId\":null,\"linkedTitle\":null,\"linkedUrl\":null,\"payload\":\"[]\",\"type\":\"entry\"}",
              "linkText": "Learn more",
              "contentAlignment": true,
              "contentTheme": "blueTheme",
              "sidebarEnabled": true
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
