    "2450860": {
      "type": "faqs",
      "enabled": true,
      "collapsed": false,
      "level": 1,
      "fields": {
        "headingSection": "Secure Remote Access FAQs",
        "faqs": {
          "2450861": {
            "type": 99,
            "fields": {
              "faqs": {
                "2450862": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "What is secure remote access?",
                    "answer": "<p>Secure remote access allows users to connect to systems, networks, and applications from anywhere while enforcing strong authentication, least privilege, and continuous monitoring. It helps replace insecure methods like VPNs or RDP.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450863": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "What is BeyondTrust Secure Remote Access?",
                    "answer": "<p>BeyondTrust Secure Remote Access includes two solutions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Privileged Remote Access (PRA):</strong> Delivers secure, VPN-less access for internal and external users with least privilege controls and integration into existing workflows.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Remote Support (RS):</strong> Enables service desks and support teams to access and support any device, on or off the network, with full auditing.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Both solutions enforce least privilege, monitor every session, and reduce attack surfaces while maintaining seamless connectivity.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450864": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "Is BeyondTrust a Zero Trust Network Access (ZTNA) solution?",
                    "answer": "<p>Yes. BeyondTrust Secure Remote Access helps enable ZTNA by enforcing least privilege, segmenting access, and monitoring every session. It replaces VPNs by providing VPN-less connectivity, supports credential injection (without exposing secrets), and ensures audited, controlled access only when needed.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450865": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "Is BeyondTrust a VPN?",
                    "answer": "<p>No, BeyondTrust is not a VPN. It provides VPN-less secure remote access, using Privileged Remote Access and Remote Support solutions to control, monitor, and secure connections without exposing networks.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450866": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "What is BeyondTrust Remote Jump Client?",
                    "answer": "<p>The BeyondTrust Jump Client is a lightweight agent that lets authorized users securely access and manage remote systems, even when those systems are unattended or outside the corporate network.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450867": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "How doe BeyondTrust Privileged Remote Access work?",
                    "answer": "<p>BeyondTrust Privileged Remote Access (PRA) delivers secure, centralized access for employees and third-party vendors to critical systems without relying on VPNs or direct connections. It enforces least privilege with just-in-time access, injects credentials without exposing them to users, and records and audits every session for visibility and compliance.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450868": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "How does BeyondTrust Remote Support work?",
                    "answer": "<p>BeyondTrust Remote Support allows service desks and IT teams to securely connect to any device or system, on any platform, from anywhere. It integrates with ITSM tools and enforces access controls, session monitoring, and audit trails.</p>"
                  }
                },
                "2450869": {
                  "type": "faq",
                  "enabled": true,
                  "collapsed": false,
                  "fields": {
                    "question": "What are the features of secure remote access solutions?",
                    "answer": "<p>BeyondTrust Secure Remote Access enforces Zero Trust by granting just-in-time access, supporting approval workflows, vaulting and injecting credentials, recording and auditing sessions, tunneling protocols, automating tasks with scripts, and integrating MFA and SSO. These capabilities replace VPNs and strengthen security by controlling and monitoring every connection.</p>"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
